data.description: This horse ranch is up and running and ready for you. Complete with a 36X40 shop that has a 8X16 office inside with a rafter clearance of 14', a 12X14 RV door, a 36"-man door, electricity, 3 RV hook ups (one 30 amps and one 50 amp), a 12X20 horse shelter with a 9' overhead clearance, 8X12 horse shelter with an 8' overhead clearance as well as a well. The water well has a new pump. This gorgeous property sits on 2 acres and is truly a slice of heaven. You will love the large front lawn and the covered front and back patio. The house has been wired for a generator. There is a water softener that will stay with the property. The washer and dryer as well as all kitchen appliances will remain with the property. Geothermal heating. The living room is large and complete with a wood burning fireplace that has a fan installed to evenly push the heat throughout the home. There is a bonus space that would be great for a second living space, large office, or formal dining room. There is laminate and tile flooring throughout. There is lots of natural light. The kitchen is a great size and has a pantry. The laundry room is a good size, has storage, and a half bathroom off of it. The bedrooms are all very large and have great closet space. The hallway bathroom is stunning from the marble tile floors to the double vanities and full tiled shower/tub. The master bedroom has two closets and an on-suite bathroom containing double vanities and a beautifully tiled shower/tub. The 2 car garage is spacious and contains a storm shelter. This property gives you the country feel while also only being 5 minutes from town and about 7 minutes to Altus Airforce Base. This is a MUST SEE.
